    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Shallow decorative vessels in a variety of materials that often have ruffled or wavy edges, and usually set in a purpose-made stand, sometimes having a handle resembling a basket. These have evolved from the more ephemeral objects used at weddings to hold flowers or the bridal bouquet.</Note_Text>
